(1, 1, '2014-05-19 18:49:55', '2014-05-19 18:49:55', 'Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!', 'Hello world!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2014-05-19 18:49:55', '2014-05-19 18:49:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
(4, 1, '2014-05-19 19:25:46', '2014-05-19 19:25:46', 'Thank you so much for, once again, providing us with a wonderful Casino Night experience.  This was the fourth time that you have so graciously traveled to Quechee for our important fund raiser.  It was such a success that we have asked you back for yet another year (2014) of fun.\r\n\r\nThe equipment that you bring is professional and attractive.  You and your staff are also professional, friendly and helpful.  You arrive on time, transform our "grill room" into a casino, train our volunteers in the art of dealing Blackjack and then take over the roulette and craps tables.  At the end of the evening, the "grill room" is restored and back to normal.  You are great to work with - thank you.\r\n\r\nOur 2013 Children''s Hospital at Dartmouth (CHaD) Atlantic City Casino Night was a big success by all accounts thanks in no small part to you and your staff.  The funds raised by this event will help support the Child Advocacy and Protection Program (CAPP) and build on the endowment we started eight years ago.  CAPP helps some of the most vulnerable children in our region - those who are the victims of neglect or abuse.\r\n\r\nOver 230 guests enjoyed our festive evening and we realized a profit of over $42,700 for the kids!  As you know we combined the profits from our Saturday night Gala with the profits from our CHaD Classic Golf Tournament (held in June).  As a result of the success of these 2 events, we (QLLA Charities, Inc.) were able to present a check for $107,000 to CHaD.  This brings our 29 year total to over $1.85 million.\r\n\r\nYour support was very instrumental in helping us to realize our significant profit for the Gala!  Please accept our heartfelt thank you for your help.\r\n\r\nSharin Luti (CHaD Gala Co-Chair)', 'Children''s Hospital Dartmouth-Hitchcock', 'The equipment that you bring is professional and attractive.  You and your staff are also professional, friendly and helpful.  You arrive on time, transform our "grill room" into a casino, train our volunteers in the art of dealing Blackjack and then take over the roulette and craps tables.  At the end of the evening, the "grill room" is restored and back to normal.  You are great to work with - thank you.  Over 230 guests enjoyed our festive evening and we realized a profit of over $42,700 for the kids!', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'childrens-hospital-dartmouth-hitchcock', '', '', '2014-06-25 20:43:12', '2014-06-25 20:43:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=4', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
