(27, 1, '2014-06-10 20:18:39', '2014-06-10 20:18:39', 'A BIG THANK YOU to you and your crew for helping me to put on what is surely to be one of the greatest nights in RAI Summit history!  Our attendees had a blast and really enjoyed themselves and time spent interacting with your staff.  They definitely made our night!  Kuddos to them!', 'Retirement Alliance, Inc.', 'A BIG THANK YOU to you and your crew for helping me to put on what is surely to be one of the greatest nights in RAI Summit history!  Our attendees had a blast and really enjoyed themselves and time spent interacting with your staff.  They definitely made our night!  Kuddos to them!', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'retirement-alliance-inc', '', '', '2014-06-25 20:16:02', '2014-06-25 20:16:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=27', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
