(29, 1, '2014-06-10 21:08:14', '2014-06-10 21:08:14', '"Maynard Music Association''s Casino Game Night was a huge success with over 80 prizes awarded to our winners.  Our success would not have been possible without the support of businesses such as you.  Thank you for making the night so much fun with the use of your gaming tables.  Over ten thousand dollars was raised from this event, which will provide scholarships, replace aging instruments and offset other miscellaneous music related expenses for both the High School and Fowler School band and chorus programs.\r\n\r\nMaynard''s High School and Fowler School bands participate in district, state and national competitions.  In addition, the band &amp; chorus perform in various concerts and parades that the public are welcome to attend.\r\n\r\nNumerous studies reveal that kids who participate in music programs perform better on tests.  Please know that your contribution made a positive impact on Maynard''s High School and Fowler School band and chorus members Thank you again for your support."', 'Maynard Music Association', '"Maynard Music Association''s Casino Game Night was a huge success with over 80 prizes awarded to our winners.  Our success would not have been possible without the support of businesses such as you.  Thank you for making the night so much fun with the use of your gaming tables.  Over ten thousand dollars was raised from this event, which will provide scholarships, replace aging instruments and offset other miscellaneous music related expenses for both the High School and Fowler School band and chorus programs."', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'maynard-music-association', '', '', '2014-07-03 19:33:30', '2014-07-03 19:33:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=29', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(30, 1, '2014-06-10 21:08:10', '2014-06-10 21:08:10', '', 'maynard', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'maynard', '', '', '2014-06-10 21:08:10', '2014-06-10 21:08:10', '', 29, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/maynard.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(31, 1, '2014-06-10 21:18:26', '2014-06-10 21:18:26', 'This year we decided to add some extra excitement to our Company Holiday party by having a "Casino Night" hosted by Alpine Amusement.  I have to admit we were slightly skeptical about how popular the games would be among our employees.  Much to our surprise the night was a huge success and we have received nothing but positive feedback from our employees.\r\n\r\n"I especially liked ''Little Las Vegas''. What a great idea!" - John W., Union Mutual Employee\r\n\r\nRon Jacobs was extremely accommodating and an overall delight to work with.  The event was shockingly affordable and covered everything including set-up and break-down of all equipment and materials.  The entire Alpine staff was very professional, experienced, helpful and pleasant throughout the night.  The only thing we will do differently in the future is provide a couple more blackjack tables (by far the most popular game) and Wheel of Fortune.  We couldn''t be more pleased with Alpine Amusement and will certainly be using their services again in the future.', 'Union Mutual of Vermont Companies', '[Alpine Amusement] was extremely accommodating and an overall delight to work with.  The event was shockingly affordable and covered everything including set-up and break-down of all equipment and materials.  The entire Alpine staff was very professional, experienced, helpful and pleasant throughout the night.  The only thing we will do differently in the future is provide a couple more blackjack tables (by far the most popular game) and Wheel of Fortune.  We couldn''t be more pleased with Alpine Amusement and will certainly be using their services again in the future.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'union-mutual-of-vermont-companies', '', '', '2014-06-25 20:15:42', '2014-06-25 20:15:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=31', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(32, 1, '2014-06-10 21:18:22', '2014-06-10 21:18:22', '', 'unionmutualvt', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'unionmutualvt', '', '', '2014-06-10 21:18:22', '2014-06-10 21:18:22', '', 31, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/unionmutualvt.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(33, 1, '2014-06-10 21:28:46', '2014-06-10 21:28:46', 'I would like to thank you both personally and on behalf of the Wolfeboro Area Children''s Center for the wonderful job you did in making our "Diamonds &amp; Denim Casino Night" fundraiser such a great event.\r\n\r\nAlpine Amusement offered the complete pacakage - the games, the chips, the helpful information cards, the training, the advice on how to run different aspects of the evening and a friendly person with whom to work.  You answered questions I didnt even know to ask and responded quickly and completely to the questions I did ask.  You made having the event so easy.\r\n\r\nIt is a challenge to find a fundraiser for a non-profit organization that hasn''t been done over and over again by other groups in our small community.  However, we found it!  Our guests had very positive comments and such a wonderful time that they want us to have the casino night again next year.  We''ll be in touch!', 'Wolfeboro Area Children''s Center', 'Alpine Amusement offered the complete package - the games, the chips, the helpful information cards, the training, the advice on how to run different aspects of the evening and a friendly person with whom to work.  It is a challenge to find a fundraiser for a non-profit organization that hasn''t been done over and over again by other groups in our small community.  However, we found it!  Our guests had very positive comments and such a wonderful time that they want us to have the casino night again next year. ', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wolfeboro-area-childrens-center', '', '', '2014-06-10 23:05:28', '2014-06-10 23:05:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=33', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(34, 1, '2014-06-10 21:28:40', '2014-06-10 21:28:40', '', 'wolfeboro-childrens', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'wolfeboro-childrens', '', '', '2014-06-10 21:28:40', '2014-06-10 21:28:40', '', 33, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/wolfeboro-childrens.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(35, 1, '2014-06-10 21:46:47', '2014-06-10 21:46:47', '"Very nice.  Best party in many years.  Food, venue, and entertainment were top notch."\r\n\r\n"I thought the party was SO great!  It''s the best one I have been to!"\r\n\r\n"Casino was great fun."\r\n\r\n"I loved the casino games and the prizes were fantastic.  It was nice to be able to talk to co-workers and spouses without having to yell above the music.  Everyone was having a blast with gambling!"\r\n\r\nThe casino is a must for next year.  It is worth every penny to see so much joy and excitement in the room and everyone so animated - everyone works so hard, they travel, they stay late - this is something that brings good morale and very worth it.\r\n\r\nThanks again for making our Holiday party such a huge success!', 'Vermont Systems', 'The casino is a must for next year.  It is worth every penny to see so much joy and excitement in the room and everyone so animated - everyone works so hard, they travel, they stay late - this is something that brings good morale and very worth it.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vermont-systems', '', '', '2014-06-25 20:15:31', '2014-06-25 20:15:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=35', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
