(43, 1, '2014-06-25 20:23:31', '2014-06-25 20:23:31', 'Our Association has utilized Alpine Amusement for the past 8+ years at our annual stockholders meeting.  We strive to build relationships and in doing so look for ways to have the attendees mingle.  To this end, we have found Casino Night to be an extremely effective tool.  We start each guest with a set amount of chips.  The highest winners then can select from prizes donated by the member companies and vendors of our Association.  Ron Jacob’s crew is wonderful in teaching people to play games that they may not normally try in a very relaxed and fun manner. \r\n \r\nOur group consist of CEOs and senior executives with spouses.  I have only heard praise for the Alpine Amusement group.  I know that several have also utilized Alpine Amusement for their respective functions.\r\n \r\nAs a point of comparison, our first event was not with Alpine Amusement.  There is literally no comparison to the professionalism and general demeanor of Ron’s group.  I would highly recommend them to anyone interested.  We have also used his group as part of a fund raiser to our school with huge success.', 'Mutual Fire Insurance Association', 'Our Association has utilized Alpine Amusement for the past 8+ years at our annual stockholders meeting.  We strive to build relationships and in doing so look for ways to have the attendees mingle.  To this end, we have found Casino Night to be an extremely effective tool.  Our group consist of CEOs and senior executives with spouses.  I have only heard praise for the Alpine Amusement group.  There is literally no comparison to the professionalism and general demeanor of Ron’s group.  I would highly recommend them to anyone interested.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mutual-fire-insurance-association', '', '', '2014-06-25 20:24:49', '2014-06-25 20:24:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=43', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
