(60, 1, '2014-07-03 19:18:34', '2014-07-03 19:18:34', 'Alpine Amusement provides Las Vegas-style casino night events for corporate entertainment and non-profit organizations.  Apline Amusement is a Vermont-based firm that travesl extensively throughout New England and northern New York to put on Casino Night events for its corporate and non profit clients.  Apline Amusement works closely with corporate event planners and meeting planners in the New England region to help customize, design and execute memorable events for its client.  Alpine Amusement has extensive gaming experience and has been in operation since 1991.  If you are looking to do something different for your company party and show how much you appreciate your employees, or if you are a fund raiser looking to innovate and try a fresh approach to maximize efficiency and meet your goals, then contact Alpine Amusement to discuss the benefits of an exciting Las Vegas style Casino Night Party.', 'Contact Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-03 19:18:34', '2014-07-03 19:18:34', '', 12, 'http://localhost:8888/wordpress/12-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
